product_name: Jouer Cosmetics Rose Cut Gems Blush & Cheek Topper Palette
user_specs: ['Eye Color Blue', 'Hair color Blonde', 'Skin Tone Light', 'Skin Type Oily']
review_content:
This palette has become something I use almost every time I do my makeup. The blushes are SUPER pigmented so make sure you use a light hand but they look gorgeous on the skin. The formula is creamy and does not cake up on the skin or transfer throughout the day. I have light skin and ALL of the colors look flattering on me and mix well with one another. The highlighter is gorgeous but definitely contains glitter which I like but I know some people don't!

user_specs: ['Eye Color Blue', 'Hair color Blonde', 'Skin Tone Fair', 'Skin Type Dry']

product_name: Jouer Cosmetics Rose Cut Gems Blush & Cheek Topper Palette

product_name: Jouer Cosmetics Rose Cut Gems Blush & Cheek Topper Palette
user_specs: ['Eye Color Hazel', 'Hair color Auburn', 'Skin Tone Fair', 'Skin Type Combination']
review_title: Beautiful Blushes Make this Palette Worth It
review_content: The blushes are beautiful. Not as pigmented as I expected, but they blend and build up nicely. I prefer it that way, because superpigmented blushes can be harder for me to work with than ones that I can gradually build up, but I can see this as not being great for darker skin tones. The topper is pure glitter, and something I would probably only use on special occasions, but the palette is still worth it for me.
